text:
Xindice 1.1b5-dev compiles on JDK 1.5 if you apply this (very tiny) patch to 
IndexManager.  I simply took 'enum' and spelled it out the three times it 
occurs.  Otherwise, the compiler (w/ 1.5 compliance) errs on the keyword being 
used as a variable name.
creator: tobrien@discursive.com
